title: About
text: I am currently a graduate student studying at the Univeristy of California, Irvine. I am obtaining my master’s degree in Business Analytics and will be graduating in June 2025. I also completed my undergraduate years at UCI where I recieved a bachelor’s degree is Economics and a minor in Business Management.
